DojoContentPane
public abstract class AbstractDojoComplexPane
extends com.google.gwt.user.client.ui.ComplexPanel
implements HasDojo

This abstract class aims to simplify the integration of a Dojo widget in GWT ComplexPane. The class implements the interface HasDojo permitting to use the DojoController. As a ComplexPanel is associated to a container element, it will have to be associated to the container element of the Dojo widget using the method setDojoContent().This method is called when the widget is attached to the browser.

Author:
Vianney
